<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1078694" n="1"/>
<opener><salute>Viro Clarissimo et toto Orbe Celeberrimo 
                            <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Johanni Bernoulli</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="persom">Petrus Antonius Michelotti</rs>.</salute></opener>
<p><rs key="B_1714-09-12_991170515019705501" type="letter">Litteras tuas</rs><note type="editorial">Brief von Johann I Bernoulli an Pietro Antonio Michelotti vom 12.09.1714.</note> humanissimas <choice><abbr>d.</abbr><expan>die</expan></choice> 12 proxim<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>teriti Men<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>sis exaratas ante octo dies ad me pervenisse Te certio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>rem facio Vir Doctissime; atque ex illis tuam ad Nos
                        <lb/>veniendi sub certis conditionibus deliberationem
                        <lb/>percepisse. Profecto Te cupimus adventumque opta<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>mus tuum. Amplissimus Moderator ac <choice><abbr>D.</abbr><expan>Divi</expan></choice> Marci
                        <lb/>Procurator <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410" type="person">Ruzzinus</rs> Eques Generosissimus simul cum
                        <lb/>duobus reliquis <choice><abbr>Illust.<hi rendition="#sup">mis</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissimis</expan></choice> et <choice><abbr>Excell.<hi rendition="#sup">is</hi></abbr><expan>Excellentissimis</expan></choice> Patavini Archilycei
                        <lb/>Moderatoribus <rs key="pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="person">Lauredano</rs> atque <rs key="pers_DE-588-1111043582" type="person">Pisano</rs> etiam <choice><abbr>D.</abbr><expan>Divi</expan></choice>
<lb/>Marci Procuratoribus et quidem magni nominis,
                        <lb/>pro Tua eximia Persona maximam <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stimationem
                        <lb/>habere mihi videtur. Isti <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">TriumViri</rs> Amplissimi it<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>
                        <lb/>mihi dispositi esse videntur ad Te solemniter vo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>candum, ut rem ex voto brevi successuram putem
                        <lb/>et quidem sine dubio postquam responsum
                        <lb/>a Te accepero pro hac, quam ad Te mitto episto<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>la<!-- brieftag (gemeint ist vorliegender Brief selbst) -->. Antequam ergo solemniter Te vocent Amplissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>mi <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Moderatores</rs> jubent ut ego ipsis exponam quid
                        <lb/>intelligas pro Thalero imperiali; petivisti etenim
                        <lb/>1500 Thaleros imperiales pro quolibet anno. Thaler<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>us imperialis h<choice><orig><g ref="#ihat">î</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice>c <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quipollet uni floreno germanico
                        <lb/>cum dimidio; hoc est parum aut nihil abest ab
                        <lb/>unico Ducato veneto. Si Tu Vir celeberrime
                        <pb facs="1078695" n="2"/>
<lb/>pro Thalero imperiali intelligis valorem unius Du<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>cati veneti, 1500 Thaleros imperiales, hoc est 1500 Du<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>catos Venetos annuatim obtinebis (spero) ab ex<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>celso Magistratu <choice><abbr>Nobiliss.<hi rendition="#sup">rum</hi></abbr><expan>Nobilissimorum</expan></choice> Patavini <rs type="organisation">Archilycei</rs>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Moderatorum</rs>. Si ver<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> intelligas pro Thalero im<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>periali valorem qui sit maior valore unius Duca<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>ti veneti,<note type="editorial">Währungen.</note> Te monitum volo, hosce <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Trium Viros</rs>
<lb/>Generosissimos simul decrevisse <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> solemni Tui
                        <lb/>vocatione abstinere: quoniam (aiunt ipsi) salarium 1500
                        <lb/>Ducatorum Venetorum est sine exemplo in <rs type="organisation">Ar<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>chilyceo Patavino</rs> quicquid fuerit de Gr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>wui<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice><note type="editorial">Zur Berufung von Johannes Georgius Graevius (1632-1703) siehe den Brief von Johann I Bernoulli an Michelotti vom 15. August 1714.</note>
<lb/>vocatione, cuius memoriam ipsi non inve<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>ni<unclear>re</unclear>m in Magistratu. Dominicum <rs key="pers_DE-588-11757645X" type="person">Gulielminum</rs> magno litterarum damno ante aliquot annos
                        <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> vivis sublatum, <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavium</rs> conduxerunt ad Ma<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>thematum <rs type="organisation">Cathedram</rs> persoluto stipendio 1000
                        <lb/>Ducatorum venetorum. Tibi autem Vir Illus<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>trissime offeruntur 1500 Ducati Veneti. Valorem
                        <lb/>unius Ducati veneti pro Imperiali Thalero habent
                        <lb/>igitur <choice><abbr>Illust.<hi rendition="#sup">i</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissimi</expan></choice> et <choice><abbr>Exc.<hi rendition="#sup">mi</hi></abbr><expan>Excellentissimi</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Moderatores</rs>. Poteris autem
                        <lb/>clarius ab <choice><abbr>Illustriss.<hi rendition="#sup">o</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissimo</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-135542286" type="person">Fratre</rs> Tuo (cui ut <rs key="B_1714-10-05_991170517052905501" type="letter">inclusam
                            <lb/>epistolam</rs><note type="editorial">Pietro Antonio Michelotti an Nikolaus Bernoulli den Älteren vom 5. Oktober 1714.</note><!-- brieftag (link zum Digitalisat: http://doi.org/10.7891/e-manuscripta-24368 ) --> exhibeas rogo) et Mercatoribus vestris
                        <lb/>rescire valorem unius Ducati veneti.</p>
<pb facs="1078696" n="3"/>
<p><lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">TriumViri</rs> <choice><abbr>Nobiliss.<hi rendition="#sup">i</hi></abbr><expan>Nobilissimi</expan></choice> Te mutuo petent <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs type="organisation">Magistratu</rs>
<lb/>vestro, rogabuntque spero ut Tibi veniam concedat <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Pa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tavium</rs> migrandi per sex annorum spatium, et
                        <lb/>ut Tibi det potestatem qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> possis vicarium substi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tuere, qui interim vices tuas peragat in ista <rs type="organisation">Universi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tate</rs> donec redieris in Patriam pristinam docendi
                        <lb/>Provinciam redauspicaturus. Promittetur insuper
                        <lb/><rs type="organisation">Magistratui</rs> vestro, nihil Tibi metuendum esse
                        <lb/>ob religionem quam istic profitemini, nullasque
                        <lb/>molestias inde fore nascituras; qua in re, et in quibus<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>cunque aliis occasionibus habebis Protectionem
                        <lb/>huius <choice><abbr>Sereniss.<hi rendition="#sup"><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></hi></abbr><expan>Serenissim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></expan></choice> et <choice><abbr>Potentiss.<hi rendition="#sup"><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></hi></abbr><expan>Potentissim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></expan></choice>. Reipublic<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> adversus qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice><pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>cunque pericula et malevolorum insidias atque
                        <lb/>obtrectationes. H<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c omnia inquam promittentur
                        <lb/><rs type="organisation">Magistratui</rs> vestro ad abitum tuum facilitan<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>dum. Verum isti TriumViri<note type="editorial"><rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410" type="person">Carlo Ruzzini</rs>, <rs key="pers_DE-588-1111043582" type="person">Alvise Pisani</rs> und <rs key="pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="person">Francesco Loredan</rs>.</note> Nobilissimi antequam
                        <lb/>Te petant <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs type="organisation">Magistratu</rs> vestro, et priusquam eum
                        <lb/>rogent ut Tibi veniam concedat ad Nos veniendi
                        <lb/>per sex annorum curriculum, certi saltem mo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>raliter esse volunt de responso favorabili; alioquin
                        <lb/>a <rs type="organisation">Magistratu</rs> vestro Te petere, ipsumque pro Tuo
                        <lb/>adventu rogare recusant; ut etenim ita se ge<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>rant, exigit excelsi Magistratus Moderatorum
                        <lb/><rs type="organisation">Archilycei Patavini</rs> decus atque maiestas. Idem
                        <pb facs="1078697" n="4"/>
<lb/>intellige pro <rs key="pers_DE-588-116082356" type="person">Rectore</rs> <rs type="organisation">Magistratus</rs> vestri, et pro <rs type="organisation">Senatu
                            <lb/>Academico</rs> vestr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <rs type="organisation">universitatis</rs>.<note type="editorial">Michelotti spricht vermutlich vom Rektor des Magistrats, weil er von paduanischen Verhältnissen auf Basler Verhältnisse in der Universitätsverwaltung schliesst; das wäre noch zu prüfen.</note></p>
<p>Ad h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c omnia Vir Doctissime quamprimum ut res<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>pondeas rogo: etenim si ad omnia favorabiliter
                        <lb/>respondebis, brevi solemniter vocaberis ab hoc Am<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>plissimo <rs type="organisation">Magistratu</rs> cum salario 1500 Ducatorum
                        <lb/>venetorum ad edocendas Mathematicas disciplinas
                        <lb/>in <rs type="organisation">Archilyceo Patavino</rs> per sex annorum spatium.
                        <lb/>Ego vero Tibi promitto ut post sex annos promo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>veatur Doctissimus Agnatus tuus <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolaus</rs>.
                        <lb/>Quod pertinet ad sumptus itinerarios, enitar ut Tibi persolvantur.</p>
<p>Maximas Tibi ago gratias pro iis qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mihi com<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>municare dignatus fuisti<note type="editorial">Michelotti verweist hier auf Johann I Bernoullis Brief vom 12. September 1714.</note> in iis qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> respiciunt
                        <lb/>methodum dimetiendi crassitiem et subtilitatem
                        <lb/>fluidorum; de quibus plurima alia petam si <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Pata<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>vium</rs> venies apud Nos commoraturus. <rs key="biblio_69NKSR46 biblio_W6BHQDM2 biblio_LUTG2JUY biblio_RTB4565Q" type="biblios">Fasciculus
                                <lb/>librorum vestrorum doctissimorum</rs><note type="editorial">Siehe das Postskriptum des Briefes vom 12. September 1714, in welchem Johann I Bernoulli Michelotti mitteilt, dass Nicolaus I ihm ein Bündel Bücher zugesandt hat, darunter Jacobs Ars Coniectandi, Johanns eigenes Essay d'une nouvelle theorie de la manoeuvre des vaisseaux sowie Montmorts Essay d'analyse sur les jeux de hazard.</note> per <rs key="place_GEO-2657896" type="place">Tigu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>rum</rs> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> celeberrimo <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnato</rs> Tuo transmissus
                        <lb/>ad meas nondum pervenit manus.</p> <closer><salute>Vale Vir
                        <lb/>Amicissime. Salarium oblatum non recusato,
                            <lb/>mihique favere non desine.</salute> <dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs>
<lb/><choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>ad diem</expan></choice> <date when="1714-10-05">5 Octobris 1714</date></dateline></closer>
</div></body></text></TEI>